        <abstract>
            <p>Answers CD’s queries on sexual characters and differences among the Urodela.</p>
            <p>Is interested in the relationship of pectoral and pelvic limbs in man and apes and has looked at reptiles and amphibians to find traces of the earlier conditions of the limbs.</p>
            <p>Asks whether CD knows any instances of deformities or pathological conditions occurring simultaneously in both sets of limbs.</p>
        </abstract>
